<Layout
  title="How to Build a Mobile App for Your Spryker Site (The Smart Way)"
  description="Want to level up engagement, retention, and long-term revenue? Build a mobile app. This article shows you how easy it is to turn your Spryker website into full-featured mobile apps, with MobiLoud."
